OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782461893
OL,3,CVan driver offers lift to help armed
OL,4,Cofficers catch suspect
OL,6,FA quick thinking east Kent van driver
OL,7,Fhas helped armed police to catch a
OL,8,Ffleeing suspect by offering a lift.
OL,10,FPraise has been heaped on the driver
OL,11,Fwho gave an impromptu lift to an armed
OL,12,Fofficers chasing a suspect in Thanet.
OL,14,FKent Police units were visiting a
OL,15,Fproperty in the High Street shortly
OL,16,Fafter midday on Tuesday 16 June 2026,
OL,17,Ffollowing reports of a serious assault
OL,18,Fin the area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
