PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782461893
OL,3,CVan driver offers lift to help armed
OL,4,Cofficers catch suspect
OL,6,FWhen officers arrived, a wanted man
OL,7,Fmanaged to evade them and fled the
OL,8,Fscene on foot, running towards Tivoli
OL,9,FRoad.
OL,11,FDuring the chase, a passing motorist
OL,12,Fstopped to help and told a pursuing
OL,13,Farmed officer to "get in the back" of
OL,14,Fhis van.
OL,16,FThe officer hopped on board and told
OL,17,Fhim, "Go, go, go! Cheers buddy, follow
OL,18,Fthat police officer." Before adding,
OL,19,F"Don't crash."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782461893
OL,3,CVan driver offers lift to help armed
OL,4,Cofficers catch suspect
OL,6,FWith the officer in the back of the
OL,7,Fvehicle, they were able to catch up
OL,8,Fwith the fleeing suspect and arrest
OL,9,Fhim soon afterwards.
OL,11,FThe good samaritan described his
OL,12,Fexperience as "quite exhilarating" and
OL,13,Fsaid he was glad to be of service.
OL,15,FThe member of the public has since
OL,16,Fbeen thanked for his actions and has
OL,17,Fbeen recommended for a commendation by
OL,18,Fthe force.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
