OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782461893
OL,3,CVan driver offers lift to help armed
OL,4,Cofficers catch suspect
OL,6,FArmed Policing Superintendent Will Lay
OL,7,Fsaid: "A violent offender who was
OL,8,Fbeing relentlessly pursued, and was
OL,9,Fseeking to evade capture, came close
OL,10,Fto losing patrols in a nearby park.
OL,12,F"However, our armed officers remained
OL,13,Fcommitted.
OL,15,F"Thanks to the quick and selfless
OL,16,Factions of this responsible and public-
OL,17,Fspirited driver, officers were able to
OL,18,Fapprehend the dangerous individual.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
