OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782461893
OL,3,CVan driver offers lift to help armed
OL,4,Cofficers catch suspect
OL,6,F"The successful arrest may not have
OL,7,Fbeen possible without the member of
OL,8,Fthe public and his vehicle.
OL,10,F"He should feel proud of his
OL,11,Fcontribution to keeping his community
OL,12,Fsafe, and we are truly grateful for
OL,13,Fhis assistance."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
